Template: atlas-server/vpn-dns
Type: string
Description: What is the DNS server for the VPN?
 Leave blank to disable the VPN.

Template: atlas-server/nginx
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Will you be using nginx?

Template: atlas-server/backend-port
Type: string
Default: 1400
Description: What port should the backend run on?
 This port should not be forwarded.

Template: atlas-server/stream-port
Type: string
Default: 1401
Description: What port should the streaming backend run on?
 This port should not be forwarded. The following 1000 ports should be open.
 If you are not using a VPN, this should be the same as the backend port.

Template: atlas-server/external-port
Type: string
Default: 443
Description: What port should nginx use?

Template: atlas-server/server-name
Type: string
Description: What is the nginx server_name (host)?

Template: atlas-server/cert-dir
Type: string
Description: Enter the directory containing the Let's Encrypt certificates.
 Leave blank to disable HTTPS.
